sentence: what are the populations of the states through which the mississippi river runs ?
sentence-with-vars: what are the populations of the states through which the river0 river runs ?
sql: select state.population from state where state.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' mississippi ' ) ;
sql-with-vars: select state.population from state where state.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' river0 ' ) ;
